; Regression test for issue #1639: Error parsing auto-xact predicate with "expr payee" (BZ#567)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1639
; Using "expr payee" in an auto-xact predicate should not produce a parse error.

= expr payee == "Grocery Store"
    Expenses:Tax    $10.00
    Assets:Wallet   $-10.00

2024/01/01 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Other Store
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
            $-170.00  Assets
            $-150.00    Cash
             $-20.00    Wallet
             $170.00  Expenses
             $150.00    Food
              $20.00    Tax
--------------------
                   0
end test
